joke from the... hallway.

224
00:10:12,712 --> 00:10:14,578
Do you like that,
Louise?
Yeah.

225
00:10:14,580 --> 00:10:16,981
Oh, it was really funny!

226
00:10:16,983 --> 00:10:19,450
