in your mouth.
- Mmm.

231
00:10:32,999 --> 00:10:33,998
Mmm, isn't that delicious?

232
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:37,434
Yeah, it really goes down easy,
doesn't it, Teddy?

233
00:10:37,436 --> 00:10:38,168
Ow.
[ Chuckles ]

234
00:10:38,170 --> 00:10:42,706
