244
00:11:18,209 --> 00:11:21,345
- Good night, Teddy.
- Good night, Linda.

245
00:11:21,347 --> 00:11:24,014
Sleep tight.
Sleep tighter, Lin.

246
00:11:24,016 --> 00:11:25,749
