Hey, guys.
[ All Screaming ]

276
00:12:58,344 --> 00:13:02,746
- What?
Do I have bed head?
- Oh, good God, Teddy.

277
00:13:02,748 --> 00:13:03,313
My beetles!
Ohh!

278
00:13:03,315 --> 00:13:06,617
