282
00:13:13,559 --> 00:13:14,858
- Yes.
- Ahh.

283
00:13:14,860 --> 00:13:16,593
Oh, God, Ted.
Does it hurt?

284
00:13:16,595 --> 00:13:17,694
Nope. Nope.
Don't worry about it.

285
00:13:17,696 --> 00:13:21,198
Teddy, you should probably
get to the hospital.
You okay to drive?

286
00:13:21,200 --> 00:13:26,170
No, I don't need a hospital.
I'll be fine. This is still
a magical weekend.

287
00:13:26,172 --> 00:13:26,603
Ahh.
You know?

288
00:13:26,605 --> 00:13:28,605
