What's for breakfast?

289
00:13:28,607 --> 00:13:31,942
- Eggs!
- Ugh! Nothing gets
to this guy.

290
00:13:31,944 --> 00:13:34,812
You! I don't know how,
but you did this.

291
00:13:34,814 --> 00:13:36,547
[ Sniffs ]
I know how she did it.

292
00:13:36,549 --> 00:13:37,781
She used my pheromones on him.

293
00:13:37,783 --> 00:13:41,285
Okay, well, uh,
Linda, everyone,
have fun in the B and B.

294
00:13:41,287 --> 00:13:43,520
I'll be downstairs
in the restaurant. Bye.

295
00:13:43,522 --> 00:13:44,388
Bye, Dad.
No!

296
00:13:44,390 --> 00:13:46,623
You deal with her!
She's out of control!

297
00:13:46,625 --> 00:13:49,893
Okay. Uh, give her
her room back.
No!

298
00:13:49,895 --> 00:13:52,496
Well, that's all I got. Bye.

299
00:13:52,498 --> 00:13:55,732
Louise!
You're grounded.
Go to your room.

300
00:13:55,734 --> 00:13:57,601
Gladly.
That's all I ever wanted.

301
00:13:57,603 --> 00:14:00,404
No, I mean my room.
Go to my room.

302
00:14:00,406 --> 00:14:05,175
