- Oh, yes, I can, Miss Missy.

303
00:14:06,244 --> 00:14:07,511
I guess you can.

304
00:14:07,513 --> 00:14:09,913
I've never seen
these beetles so aroused.

305
00:14:09,915 --> 00:14:11,915
I have that affect
on beetles.
[ Chuckles ]

306
00:14:11,917 --> 00:14:13,617
I haven't had this
much action in a while.

307
00:14:13,619 --> 00:14:16,820
Are they gonna call me
tomorrow? Probably not,
right? That's okay.

308
00:14:16,822 --> 00:14:22,526
Teddy, making jokes,
covered with bugs.
You are a man! Damn you!

309
00:14:22,528 --> 00:14:23,927
