Does anything get to you?

310
00:14:23,929 --> 00:14:25,495
[ Teddy ]
There's really only one thing.

311
00:14:25,497 --> 00:14:27,931
[ Gene, Tina ] Yeah?
[ Teddy ]
Costumed characters.

312
00:14:27,933 --> 00:14:30,567
You know, like the ones
