go to birthday parties.

317
00:14:41,513 --> 00:14:42,679
[ Gene ]
All right.

318
00:14:42,681 --> 00:14:43,513
Thank you, Teddy.

319
00:14:43,515 --> 00:14:48,452
Oh, thank you, Mom's purse.
Well, thank you, phone.

320
00:14:48,454 --> 00:14:50,354
Yes, I will make a call.

321
00:14:50,356 --> 00:14:51,488
♪ [ Whistling ]

322
00:14:51,490 --> 00:14:54,691
Oh, I gotcha.
Oh, you're sizzling.

323
00:14:54,693 --> 00:14:55,692
I love your sounds.

324
00:14:55,694 --> 00:14:58,462
Oh, hello.
You have costumed
characters, right?

325
00:14:58,464 --> 00:14:59,897
♪ [ Whistling ]
Oh, that's great.

326
00:14:59,899 --> 00:15:03,467
I'll take the hippo,
the fox.
Here's a cookie.

327
00:15:03,469 --> 00:15:04,401
Here's a cookie.
A baby bear.

328
00:15:04,403 --> 00:15:05,569
Here's a cookie.
And do take a credit card?

329
00:15:05,571 --> 00:15:10,007
