347
00:15:59,658 --> 00:16:00,924
Bacon.
One syllable.

348
00:16:00,926 --> 00:16:02,292
No, two syllables.
Two syllables.

349
00:16:02,294 --> 00:16:05,762
Oink, oink, oink, oink,
oink, oink, oink, oink!
Uh, a pig.

350
00:16:05,764 --> 00:16:06,930
Dinosaur.
Bacon!

351
00:16:06,932 --> 00:16:08,732
Bacon burger.
Kevin Bacon.

352
00:16:08,734 --> 00:16:10,434
Second word.
Burger.

353
00:16:10,436 --> 00:16:12,469
Brake pads?
[ Moos ]

354
00:16:12,471 --> 00:16:14,104
Dinosaur.
Jurassic Park!

355
00:16:14,106 --> 00:16:15,339
[ Moos ]
Charades!

356
00:16:15,341 --> 00:16:17,708
You can't guess charades.
Yes, you can.

357
00:16:17,710 --> 00:16:18,909
Oh. Is it charades?

358
00:16:18,911 --> 00:16:21,545
[ Moos ]
Cow. Burger!
Bacon burger!

359
00:16:21,547 --> 00:16:24,448
All right.
Yes. Bacon burger!
All right. I can do that.

360
00:16:24,450 --> 00:16:28,485
[ Doorbell Rings ]
Uh, doorbell.
I'll get it.

361
00:16:28,487 --> 00:16:29,619
Oh, Footloose.

362
00:16:29,621 --> 00:16:31,989
Can I--
Can I help you?

363
00:16:31,991 --> 00:16:33,724
