369
00:16:47,038 --> 00:16:53,043
- Someone's excited to see
the Fuzzy Buddies.
- [ Screams ]

370
00:16:53,045 --> 00:16:53,977
Don't!
No, no, no!

371
00:16:53,979 --> 00:16:57,414
Whoa.
You're a big boy-- Ohh!

372
00:16:59,717 --> 00:17:03,120
[ Teddy Grunting ]
Oh, my God!

373
00:17:03,122 --> 00:17:05,622
Teddy.
Ohh! Ahh!

374
00:17:05,624 --> 00:17:08,992
