379
00:17:22,107 --> 00:17:23,840
Bob, do you have
my bacon burger?

380
00:17:23,842 --> 00:17:26,743
Oh, yeah,
the bacon burger. Here.
Oh.

381
00:17:26,745 --> 00:17:29,446
Bob, can you help me?
I can't chew.

382
00:17:29,448 --> 00:17:31,715
You need me to feed you?
Yeah.

383
00:17:31,717 --> 00:17:34,084
Chew it up for him,
like a mama bird.

384
00:17:34,086 --> 00:17:35,986
Linda, no!
He's platinum status!

385
00:17:35,988 --> 00:17:39,589
You're crazy, Linda!
It's all right, guys.
I got it.

386
00:17:39,591 --> 00:17:41,458
Perfect guest.

387
00:17:42,894 --> 00:17:46,963
So let me get this straight.
Teddy beat up a bunch
of giant animals.

388
00:17:46,965 --> 00:17:51,668
