and then you locked the guests
in their rooms?

389
00:17:51,670 --> 00:17:55,439
They were gonna leave before
the big ice cream social
at 3:00.

390
00:17:55,441 --> 00:17:58,875
Lin, just give me
the key, all right?
I'm gonna let them out.

391
00:17:58,877 --> 00:17:59,576
No.
Yes.

392
00:17:59,578 --> 00:18:03,880
No.
Look at yourself. Look at
what you've turned into!

393
00:18:03,882 --> 00:18:04,881
Oh, all right.

394
00:18:04,883 --> 00:18:08,618
All I wanted was a charming
bed and breakfast, that's all.

395
00:18:08,620 --> 00:18:12,622
Now what am I gonna say
to God when I go to heaven?

396
00:18:12,624 --> 00:18:16,093
Ohh! Oh! Uh-oh.
I lost the key!

397
00:18:16,095 --> 00:18:18,795
Oh, my God,
what have I done?

398
00:18:18,797 --> 00:18:20,497
All right, all right,
listen.

399
00:18:20,499 --> 00:18:22,032
You know,
Louise picks locks.

400
00:18:22,034 --> 00:18:25,602
- Louise hates me.
- No, she doesn't
hate you, Lin.

401
00:18:25,604 --> 00:18:30,140
I'm sure she's broken
out of our room already.
Oh.

402
00:18:31,042 --> 00:18:34,744
I'm gonna go
deal with Teddy.
Why don't you try her room?

403
00:18:34,746 --> 00:18:36,446
Okay.

404
00:18:37,448 --> 00:18:40,050
Hi, honey. It's Mommy.

405
00:18:40,052 --> 00:18:42,519
Oh, hello, Mother.
Please do come in.

406
00:18:42,521 --> 00:18:47,824
Louise, I'm sorry
I rented your room to Teddy and
then locked you in our bedroom.

407
00:18:47,826 --> 00:18:49,025
