412
00:19:01,039 --> 00:19:04,241
[ Sighs ]
I would just
cut it up right now.

413
00:19:04,243 --> 00:19:05,142
Oh. No, not that.

414
00:19:05,144 --> 00:19:09,479
Will you please help me
get Javeed and the Samuels
out of their rooms?

415
00:19:09,481 --> 00:19:12,549
I locked them in and I--
I kind of lost the key.

416
00:19:12,551 --> 00:19:15,619
There might be something
I can do.

417
00:19:16,921 --> 00:19:20,524
Javeed, I'm sorry
I locked you in your room.

418
00:19:20,526 --> 00:19:21,958
You're free to go
if you wish.

419
00:19:21,960 --> 00:19:24,694
- You locked me in my room?
- No.

420
00:19:24,696 --> 00:19:26,897
She's completely bonkers,
isn't she?

421
00:19:26,899 --> 00:19:29,499
Look at me when
I'm talking to you!

422
00:19:31,135 --> 00:19:34,771
