How did they get
out of a locked room?

423
00:19:34,773 --> 00:19:37,541
It was their greatest escape.

424
00:19:38,910 --> 00:19:42,546
Look what they left behind.
Look. My tongue is trapped.

425
00:19:42,548 --> 00:19:44,748
Now it's escaped.
Now it's trapped.

426
00:19:44,750 --> 00:19:46,183
Now it's escaped.
Hey, look!

427
00:19:46,185 --> 00:19:47,717
They're still
climbing down.

428
00:19:47,719 --> 00:19:50,854
You two all right?
You need any help
with your bags?

429
00:19:50,856 --> 00:19:54,024
No. Uh, actually we're stuck.
Please help us.

430
00:19:54,026 --> 00:19:55,859
I suppose
we could get a ladder.

431
00:19:55,861 --> 00:19:58,562
How much did you
like my B and B?
A lot.

432
00:19:58,564 --> 00:20:00,864
Are you gonna recommend us
to your friends?
Yes!

433
00:20:00,866 --> 00:20:04,868
