Thanks a lot.

438
00:20:12,611 --> 00:20:16,680
I don't know what to tip
in this situation.
Yeah. Not two dollars.

439
00:20:16,682 --> 00:20:17,914
Oh, hey, Teddy.
Uh, you all right?

440
00:20:17,916 --> 00:20:21,985
I think I worked through
my issues, Bob. Me and the owl
