441
00:20:21,987 --> 00:20:24,588
I'm pretty sure
there's a woman inside.
[ Chuckles ]

442
00:20:24,590 --> 00:20:26,856
That's a guy, Teddy.
Oh, that's a woman.

443
00:20:26,858 --> 00:20:28,091
The owl was a guy.
It's a woman.

444
00:20:28,093 --> 00:20:31,261
The fox was a girl.
Oh. Did the fox
leave already?

445
00:20:31,263 --> 00:20:35,765
Yes.
Oh. Linda, you are
a delightful hostess.

446
00:20:35,767 --> 00:20:38,768
Ah, thanks, Teddy.
See you at lunch, Bob.

447
00:20:38,770 --> 00:20:44,040
Well, that was all right.
It was pretty good.
I give us a B.

448
00:20:44,042 --> 00:20:45,575
Mmm.
